quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,"Haa, miim."
  44,2,"Mi woo…óndirii defere …ďanngunde nde !"
  44,3,"Min njippinirii nde e jemma barkinaa…óo, Min siforii won'de jeertinoo…ďe."
  44,4,"Ko e on (jehma) woni ko seerndetee kala fiyaaku √Īe√Īaa…óo."
  44,5,"∆äuum ko yamiroore immorde ka amen. Min siforii won'de Nuloo…ďe."
  44,6,"yurmeende immornde ka Joomi maa. Pellet, ko KaŇčko woni Nanoowo, ganndu…óo oon."
  44,7,"Jey…óo kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndiin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si wonii ko on yananaa…ďe."
  44,8,"Dewetee…óo goo alaa, si wanaa KaŇčko. Homo wuurna, Himo wara. Jey…óo on Jeyi baabiraa…ďe mon aram…ďe …ďeen."
  44,9,"Ko woni tan, …ďe wonii e sikke, he…ďe pija."
  44,10,"Habbito √Īande kammu ngun ardata e curki fee√Īuuki,"
  44,11,"suddayki yim…ďe …ďen. [∆Āe mbi'anee]: ""∆äuum ko lepte mu'usuu…óe"" !"
  44,12,"""Joomi amen, huncan min lepte …óeen. Minen ko men gooŇč…óin…ďe""."
  44,13,"Ko honno …ďe mbaajitorta, ko goongo Nulaa…óo …ďanngin…óo ariino …ďe?"
  44,14,"Refti …ďe nduŇčti, …ďe mb'i: ""Ko tinndinaa…óo, kaangaa…óo""."
  44,15,"Awa ko Min ittoo…ďe lepte …óen see…óa; kono pellet, ko on ruttitotoo…ďe."
  44,16,"√Ďande Min nanngiroyta bippannde mawnde nden, pellet, ko Min yo…ďtoytoo…ďe."
  44,17,"GooŇč…óii Min njarribinoke ado ma…ď…ďe, yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďen, Nulaa…óo teddu…óo ari e ma…ď…ďe,"
  44,18,"won'de: ""mba…óee e juu…óe am, jiyaa…ďe Allah …ďeen. Min ko mi Nulaa…óo e mon, koolnii…óo."
  44,19,"E won'de wota on townitano Allah, tawde mi addanay on hujja …ďanngu…óo."
  44,20,"Min kadi noon, mi moolorii Jey…óo kam oon Jeyi on, nde pi…óotonmi kaa∆īe."
  44,21,"Si on ngooŇč…óinaa kam, haray celee kam""."
  44,22,"O noddi Joomi makko, won'de: ""∆Āee …óoo, ko yim…ďe bon…ďe""."
  44,23,"""Yaadir e jiyaa…ďe Am …ďen jehma; nganndon ko on sukketee…ďe."
  44,24,"Ngaccaa maayo ngoon dee∆īa [si on lummbii] …ďeya kan, ko konu yooleteengu""."
  44,25,"∆äuu…óii ko …ďe ngacci e gese e …ďulli,"
  44,26,"e remuruuji e ko…óan'de teddu…óe,"
  44,27,"e dokke …ďe ngonnoo e neeminireede."
  44,28,"Ko wano noon. Hooti Min ndonini …ói yim…ďe wo…ď…ďe."
  44,29,"Kammu nguun to…ďaali …ďe, wonaa leydi ndin, …ďe ngonaani kadi mu√Īantee…ďe."
  44,30,"GooŇč…óii Min nda…óndii …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďeen e lepte koyneeje;"
  44,31,"immorde e Fir'awna, tawde o laatino townitii…óo, jiyaa…óo e fantim…ďe …ďeen."
  44,32,"GooŇč…óii Min cu…ďorike …ďe e dow ganndal e hoore winndere ndeen,"
  44,33,"Min ngokki …ďe Ma'andeeji, …ói jarrabuyee …ďanngu…óo woni e mum."
  44,34,"∆Āee kan no mbi'a:"
  44,35,"""Ndee wonaani, si wonaa maayde amen aranere nden tan. Min wonatah immintinoytee…ďe."
  44,36,"Awa artiree baabiraa…ďe amen …ďeen, si wonii ko on gooŇč…óu…ďe""."
  44,37,"Kere ko kam…ďe …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude kaa ko yim…ďe ""Tubba'in"" …ďeen e …ďeya adinoo…ďe …ďe? Min kalkuno …ďeen, tawde hari ko …ďe bon…ďe."
  44,38,"Min tagiraali kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, fijoo…ďe."
  44,39,"Min tagiraali …óin …ói…ói, si wonaa e goonga. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe nganndaa."
  44,40,"Pellet, ko √Ďalaande Seerndindiro ngon, woni ko …ďe saatinanaa, kam…ďe fof."
  44,41,"√Ďalnde nde gi…óo duncanoytaa gi…óo [mum] hay hu'unde; …ďe wonaani kadi walloytee…ďe,"
  44,42,"si wonaa mo Allah yurmaa woo. Pellet, ko KaŇčko woni poolu…óo, jurmotoo…óo On."
  44,43,"Pellet, lekki Zaqquumi Kini."
  44,44,"ko √Īaametee bakkodin…ďe …ďeen."
  44,45,"A sikkay ko taayinaa ; hino fata ka ndeer deedi."
  44,46,"Wano ngul…óam fatirta."
  44,47,"Nanngee mo poo…óiron ka hakkunde dul…ďatnge."
  44,48,"refti njuppon ka hoore makko, lepte patinaa…óe …óeen."
  44,49,"Mee…óu noon ! Asn [sikkunoo…óo] ko a pool…óo, teddu…óo."
  44,50,"Awa ko …óuum woni kon ko cikkiti…óon e mum."
  44,51,"Pellet, gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďren ngonii e weerde koolniinde,"
  44,52,"e ndeer gese e …ďulli,"
  44,53,"he…ďe …ďoornoo ko …óaati e ko tekki, hara hi…ďe peewtondiri."
  44,54,"Ko wano noon. Min ndesini …ďe kadi yaac…ďe gite."
  44,55,"Hi…ďe nodda toon, kala muuyantee…ói, hara ko …ďe hoolii…ďe."
  44,56,"∆Āe mee…óataa toon maayde, si wonaa maayde aranere nden. O da…ónda …ďe lepte Jahiimi …óeen."
  44,57,"ko dokkal noon, immorde ka Joomi maa. Awa ko …óuum woni maloore mawnde ndeen."
  44,58,"Ko Min newiniri nde e …óamngal maa…óa, ko no …ďe mbaajitora."
  44,59,"Habito. Kam…ďe ne ko …ďe habbitii…ďe."
